/futures/HSI\" target=\"_blank\">\u671f\u6307\u5c08\u9801</a>\u3002</p>   </div>\n        ", "link": "https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/3945473/%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%9F%E5%A0%B119750+%E8%B7%8C61%E9%BB%9E"}]}